snippet.textDisplay: I'm writing this message just for Xulfi Bhai, I hope this message reaches him. After listening to 2:Am, I just cannot hold back my tears. I don't know how every time you touch us so deeply. Every word Star Shah is spitting is facts & truth. After one experiences a heartbreak, he or she feels useless, used, and unwanted, and then Zeeshan is showing us the good part when in real life our tarbiyat comes and makes us believe in good things again. Our creator makes us believe in everything good. Love is pure whether you find it in humanity, family, or in Allah's plan. HE always reminds us k MAI LOGON KI ASLIYAT DIKHA KR PUCHUNGA K TUMHARA OR KON HAI MERE ELAWA. Zulfi Bhai, you have outdone yourself. This is a masterpiece; both singers are incredible and the aesthetics are on point. I have no words to describe what I'm feeling right now. My tears keep falling. Thank you Coke Studio❤
